message: Add index modules for library versions
Decouple styled-system from concrete css-in-js libraries
Add support for dot notation in color keys

Add repository to package.json

This will add the link on the npm page as well as make octolinker work when clicking on styled-system.
Add getter helper and pseudo styles

Merge pull request #67 from Andarist/patch-1

Add peerDependency on react
Configure ava to play nice with es module syntax
Spike out a script for all package testing
Run npm i if ci env
Ignore examples dir in code coverage

Distribute esm with module field

We found some interop problems with `mjs` dual mode. It's probably
better to be consistent and solve the problem with `module` field
like I did in rebass.
Fix missing functions in styles export

Merge pull request #287 from TrySound/module-field

Distribute esm with module field
Add inline style tag for logo animations
Merge branch 'babel-runtime' of https://github.com/TrySound/styled-system into TrySound-babel-runtime

Update system-docs to handle v4 styled-components

Styled components are no longer functions, but objects with a
render function. This updates the check to also allow these
new components by checking for the render function.

Merge pull request #317 from m0xx/add-crossenv

Add cross-env to build on Windows
Remove packages scripts and update docs
feat(space): allow nested objects in space

Merge pull request #396 from jxnblk/v4

V4 docs
Fix props for textStyles and colorStyles - fixes #403
Remove benchmarking and clean up package.json
initialize lerna and create single styled-system package folder
